Toy experiments while learning OpenGL

Code written while following learnopengl.com, all props to Joey de Vries.

Dependencies:
If in debian/ubuntu:
$ sudo apt-get install python3 ninja-build meson
$ sudo apt-get install libglew-dev libglfw3-dev

If in fedora:
$ sudo dnf install ninja-build meson
$ sudo dnf install glew-devel glfw-devel

Build:
$ meson builddir && cd builddir
$ ninja
$ ./hello
